{"tid":2060212,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)潛行兇間 十三猛鬼 狙魔人","createTime":"2020-06-11T13:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T10:06:47.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"276e9c357307a842940f2193f7aafc714576da94","tid":2060212,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:05:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=b812fde2\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=2e2db07b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=4316abe6\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/7f/Inception_ver3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F7f%2FInception_ver3.jpg&h=5f1f2cea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images2.fanpop.com/images/photos/7600000/Thir13en-Ghosts-wallpaper-thir13en-ghosts-7671499-1680-1050.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages2.fanpop.com%2Fimages%2Fphotos%2F7600000%2FThir13en-Ghosts-wallpaper-thir13en-ghosts-7671499-1680-1050.jpg&h=8b5e2422&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/55/Van_Helsing_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F55%2FVan_Helsing_poster.jpg&h=b72c2fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.唐姆&middot;柯柏（Dominick &quot;Dom&quot; Cobb；李奧納多&middot;狄卡皮歐飾）是一名「盜夢者」（extractor），與搭檔亞瑟（Arthur）利用潛意識進入別人夢境竊取商業機密。於一次任務中，柯柏與亞瑟入侵日本國際企業老闆齋藤（Saito）的夢境意識，但柯柏的已故妻子茉兒（Mal）於夢中出現使任務失敗..<br />\n<br />\n2.等他們看到這座宏偉的宅院時簡直不敢相信自己的好運氣，雖說位置有點荒僻，但這哪裡是屋子，簡直就是一座城堡，巨大的庭院，蔥鬱的灌木，高大的建築，還有屋子裡面迷宮般數不清的房間迴廊，讓人看得眼花繚亂。<br />\n<br />\n3.凡赫辛為教會委託獵殺異種魔物的獵人，於接受教會委託協助一家族對抗吸血殭屍，之後捲入狼人、科學怪人和德古拉間的風波&hellip;結果竟發現此項任務似乎是命運對其身世的安排&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n9 10PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=5dc3b0ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=ebfaca53\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1